fields.title_en: Proceedings of the Pacific regional peer review on Stock assessment for Pacific Ocean Perch in Areas 3CD and 5DE (British Columbia); and A Simultaneous Stock Assessment of Five Rockfishes in British Columbia Waters: Splitnose, Greenstriped, Redstripe, Harlequin and Sharpchin Rockfish; November 6-9, 2012
